{"tid":2371600,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是靚午 宮保雞丁","createTime":"2021-01-19T04:07:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-20T02:12:15.000Z","uid":33359,"like":25,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"7ce6b9edc87f6fc43783510e4878911b12a234f4","tid":2371600,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T04:07:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WDsZS12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWDsZS12.jpg&h=0f0845c6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QC7CEG6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQC7CEG6.jpg&h=41243be3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n講吓味道先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見佢有落咁多香辛料<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又紅蔥頭又辣椒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食落香氣都夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n調味有微酸微辣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都幾到位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雞肉肉質都唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲係嫩口<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n面個啲花生粒唔夠香脆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n差咗啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最大缺點係一味咁送飯既餸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢俾勁少飯我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n吊住條癮真是好唔c伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"461f6ad90147d466ecd78387c385a4e982d0b495","tid":2371600,"uid":312130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T04:08:17.000Z","msg":"邊度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e215ff686a12d06a59ca83eaf892294980ada39","tid":2371600,"uid":321194,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":